MasterChef UK - Series 12, Episode 7




It's the third week of heats and five more hopefuls try to prove to judges John Torode and Gregg Wallace that they have the potential to be the 2016 MasterChef Champion. In this heat, the contestants must attempt to impress 2006 finalists Dean Edwards and Daksha Mistry, together with 2009 champion Mat Follas.




Original Air Date: 06-Apr-2016
